WEBVTT

00:13:28.244 --> 00:13:30.108
They have nothing to be ashamed of.

00:13:33.827 --> 00:13:36.550
We have seen advances
in every aspect of our lives --

00:13:36.574 --> 00:13:37.952
except our humanity.

00:13:38.523 --> 00:13:42.962
There are 65.3 million people
who have been forced out of their homes

00:13:42.986 --> 00:13:44.230
because of war --

00:13:44.685 --> 00:13:46.534
the largest number in history.

00:13:47.110 --> 00:13:49.167
We are the ones who should be ashamed.

00:13:49.712 --> 00:13:50.867
Thank you.

00:13:50.891 --> 00:13:57.420
(Applause)